---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Services">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-24">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight lg:text-6xl">Our Signature Services</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-gray-600">Tailored, physician-guided treatments to help you achieve your wellness goals.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 md:mt-24 md:grid-cols-1">
      <div class="group relative flex flex-col items-center gap-8 md:flex-row">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">A Smarter, Safer Path to Weight Loss.</h2>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--dusty-blue)]">Medically Supervised Weight Loss</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
            Our cornerstone service is a comprehensive, medically supervised weight loss program tailored to you. Your journey begins with a thorough consultation and health
            assessment with our physician. Based on this, we may prescribe FDA-approved medications, such as GLP-1s (like Ozempic or Wegovy), to support your body’s natural
            processes.
          </p>
          <a class="mt-6 inline-block font-bold text-[var(--soma-gold)] transition-all group-hover:tracking-wider" href="#">Learn More →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="relative h-80 w-full flex-shrink-0 md:w-1/2">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-xl">
            <img alt="Serene clinic interior" class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC1DqF4kEQkXeYsooWiUcoIBTapbWvghoItS72KxPzaKJNFHq2vIT-vgg-kvRGN_Y0vKVu_SMPpo-aSPzlqsCg3m6bK7NV1tGPR8Csa0cUhPrpB1F37qrzNq4OKUzMWjO_Kiaq9SsBeQmmGDfcJ70LDAGNCY-l50zRnbJm_nxmOMLYxU1YEwfjKk9rq7hR0_2zG40NJnlhN2m3oh7KeIlnJHu0W6OIT-_njC7hA26lq3G-cYZrUc2pep4TtzBxGgoYR7RUQ4v4_47jW"/>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="group relative mt-16 flex flex-col items-center gap-8 md:mt-24 md:flex-row-reverse">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">Build Muscle & Reduce Fat, All at Once.</h2>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--sage-green)]">Emsculpt Neo</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
            Emsculpt Neo is the first and only non-invasive body shaping procedure that provides simultaneous fat elimination and muscle building in a single 30-minute
            session. It’s the perfect, FDA-cleared solution for contouring the abdomen, buttocks, arms, and thighs with no downtime.
          </p>
          <a class="mt-6 inline-block font-bold text-[var(--soma-gold)] transition-all group-hover:tracking-wider" href="#">Learn More →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="relative h-80 w-full flex-shrink-0 md:w-1/2">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-xl">
            <img alt="Patient relaxing during a treatment" class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDwl4hP_aTlk6XscxRvU3du1FuYaP7olepfAHnRI72dPDdfH8zOBzGrlIzaEYSivTcLOf0d-sgI1cbLHsP9vo2lUbtfTUQcwsENZcdYdABYexjSaRgzVnzjWI3_fcibY5Gko0hLmbvvYE-VwUQIhCTJvgfsBq01g6YmYRKrcX1U_V8jqMklPtLJ9GoOcKty27HYyxRzmirOEQqmWjg12ZaZoQia6_tQGlizQymB1fa0WVyqBNwzwhn2uozmF36Mf1oT6j6ea45OTDe0"/>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="group relative mt-16 flex flex-col items-center gap-8 md:mt-24 md:flex-row">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">Replenish, Re-energize, and Renew from Within.</h2>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--dusty-blue)]">Hydration & IV Therapy</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
            Optimal hydration and nutrient levels are critical for a healthy metabolism and effective weight loss. Our targeted IV hydration therapies are designed to support
            your body on a cellular level to help boost your energy, enhance recovery, and support detoxification.
          </p>
          <a class="mt-6 inline-block font-bold text-[var(--soma-gold)] transition-all group-hover:tracking-wider" href="#">Learn More →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="relative h-80 w-full flex-shrink-0 md:w-1/2">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-xl">
            <img alt="IV therapy bag in a calm setting" class="h-full w-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB954AjRDIp109Ht-bbZmq_fi0_CCU9Ui-OXhj1Fh41Lggh1SwnRA1s3SCt5EQ7ckbMZXsxkWbwBo33YTJxvq5hPZiEo6Zbed2RCLD5s8kE9qE6INm9YbwwuO3kf7vnK4q939ngtZTbOO7ZNjFhV511B-f3t64KEwxl69vKUVOPxb7tNsGWo7RNPHnGGLQgKdc2V44iP_ohMeHDKzdACexluJyR1t4KZqXIVZRZwCJhOaKOeL4f92SvU5n4kEmFOWNEfE4ujCUh1FdH"/>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>